## §G. Control-M server mesh (new — resolves v2 §11 Q3)

Control-M folders are hosted on 4–5 specific servers (P12, P14, P32, P33, …). Each folder lives on exactly one server; folders are not duplicated across servers.

```
:ControlMServer {name:"P12"|"P14"|"P32"|"P33"|...}
:JobFolder      -[:RUNS_ON]-> :ControlMServer
:ControlMServer -[:INSTANCE_OF]-> :SwoClass {iri:"http://www.ebi.ac.uk/swo/...Platform"}
```

`:RUNS_ON` carries a `since` timestamp so server migrations are auditable. From the BMC schema (§G next), `DEF_TABLES.DATA_CENTER` is the source field for this — load it as a property on the folder, then dedupe to `:ControlMServer` nodes.

