6. **M5 — OpenLineage path** (2 days): event ingester + reconciliation + PROV projection (per v2 §4.3 unchanged).
7. **M6 — Streamlit** (4 days): all pages from §L; Application Detail and Support Team by App land first.
8. **M7 — KGoT seams** (1 day): `kg.client`, `:Thought` label, agent-id provenance.

